with 50 cents in my pocket,

00:00:47.593 --> 00:00:49.885
I ended up in Baidoa, Somalia.

00:00:50.615 --> 00:00:52.885
Journalists called it the "city of death."

00:00:53.299 --> 00:00:55.123
